properties.areaDesc: Bays and Waterways from Baffin Bay to Port Aransas; Coastal waters from Baffin Bay to Port Aransas out 20 NM
properties.headline: Marine Weather Statement issued January 15 at 9:17PM CST by NWS Corpus Christi TX
properties.description:
Moist onshore flow will continue to produce fog tonight and
Thursday morning. Visibilities will generally range from 2 to 5
nautical miles, with patchy dense fog of 1 nautical mile or less
at times.

Mariners over the Bay Waters and over the Nearshore Coastal
Waters within 20 nautical miles offshore are urged to prepare for
rapidly changing visibilities.

NWSheadline: PATCHY DENSE FOG POSSIBLE AGAIN TONIGHT
